caption:
&quot;Finals are here, but don't worry--we've got some laughs and resources to help you get through it! Take advantage of these events to help you stay motivated and supported:

❤️ STUDY FOR FINALS AT WLRC
Need a quiet and supportive space to prepare for finals? Stop by WLRC for a cozy and productive study session! Free snacks &amp; drinks!
Mon 12/9 - Fri 12/13
10am - 4pm
1700 SSB

💙 FREE FINALS CARE PACKAGES
Visit our table at SCE to grab a care package filled with treats, study tips, and affirmations!
Mon 12/9 and Wed 12/11
11am - 2pm
Student Center East Concourse

.

[ID 1: A penguin plush toy with a look of disbelief and the text reads, &quot;Me staring at notes I haven’t looked at since syllabus week.&quot;

ID 2: A person is looking frustrated out of a window. The text reads, &quot;Me watching everyone else enjoy life while I’m stuck writing my final paper.&quot;

ID 3: A yellow circular object slumped in a chair. The text reads, &quot;Me sitting there wondering if dropping out and becoming a TikTok influencer is still an option.&quot;

ID 4: A robot with a blank, neutral face staring ahead: The text reads, &quot;When you realize the final is cumulative and you only studied the last two lectures,&quot;

ID 5: A man with a confused expression: The text reads, &quot;Me after opening any exam and reading the first question.&quot;

ID 6: SpongeBob nervously holding a pencil in a classroom: The text reads, &quot;Me trying to hit the word count by adding ‘however’ and ‘therefore’ in every sentence.&quot;

ID 7: Two friends are embracing on a couch, and one looks sad and protective. The text reads, &quot;My friends trying to stop me from having a breakdown after the 4th all-nighter.&quot;

ID 8: A student studying at a desk with headphones on to promote the &quot;Study for Finals at WLRC&quot; event with bright, calming colors and study-focused imagery.

ID 9: A student holding books with bold text offering encouragement: Highlights the &quot;Finals Care Package&quot; event, with playful colors and shapes listing treats, affirmations, and tips. ]

.

