caption:
&quot;Who's ready for Thanksgiving break? Hope you’re able to make time to relax, eat some good food, and hang out with loved ones!

Special note: The UIC Pop-up Pantry is open 10am - 4pm today at the Montgomery Ward Gallery in Student Center East! Check out @uicwellnesscenter’s most recent post for details! 

.

[ID 1: A red M&amp;M lies on the ground, clearly distressed, as a yellow M&amp;M crouch to console it. The text above reads: &quot;The mashed potatoes checking on the cranberry sauce after getting passed around 20 times but still untouched.&quot;

ID 2: A mischievous cartoon character with exaggerated ears and a sly grin listens intently. The text above reads, &quot;Me listening in from the kitchen as my relatives debate politics over the Thanksgiving table.&quot;

ID 3: A stern-looking animated character with dramatic features stares intensely. The text above reads: &quot;When someone says the turkey is 'a little dry,' and it was YOUR turkey.&quot;

ID 4: Two prairie dogs, one patting the other on the shoulder, with one saying, &quot;Hol up, let him cook.&quot; The text above reads: &quot;When your aunt who usually brings drinks says she’s making the mac and cheese this year.&quot;

ID 5: Jimmy Butler squinting at a piece of paper in a basketball setting. The text reads: &quot;Me analyzing my plate trying to decide if I can go back for seconds without looking greedy.&quot;

ID 6: A character from a children’s show looks over their shoulder suspiciously in a kitchen. The text above reads: &quot;When someone says 'save me some leftovers,' and you know you’re taking the whole plate home.&quot;

ID 7: A distressed SpongeBob in a hallway with the text &quot;please say sike.&quot; The text above reads: &quot;When you show up to Thanksgiving dinner and find out there’s no mac and cheese this year.&quot;

ID 8: A boy holding a camcorder with an amused expression. The text above reads: &quot;When you’re recording Grandma’s iconic Thanksgiving rant for future generations.&quot;

ID 9: A child strapped into a seat looks side-eyed with a concerned expression. The text above reads: &quot;When they tell me to wait for everyone else before I get my plate.&quot;]

.

#UICWLRC #UICBound #UICLife #UICCAN #ThisIsUIC #UICFlames #UIC #ThanksgivingBreak&quot;.

